{"tid":2311620,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"出院後送政府部門工作  潑墨女拍片控訴「我沒有精神病」","createTime":"2020-12-04T08:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T08:37:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"259a94ae3379ec217ffd484af2aa7cef340ebed3","tid":2311620,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T08:14:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201202/MLF3W4QDZRCPRCDSWAZTQAIM3E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201202%2FMLF3W4QDZRCPRCDSWAZTQAIM3E%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGGqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=31bfd4c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201202%2FMLF3W4QDZRCPRCDSWAZTQAIM3E%2F&h=93ebc165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201202/MLF3W4QDZRCPRCDSWAZTQAIM3E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n出院後送政府部門工作 <br />\n潑墨女拍片控訴「我沒有精神病」<br />\n<br />\n曾向國家主席習近平肖像潑墨的女子董瑤瓊，今年中第二度被關押精神病院後，首次發佈公開影片。她在片中表示自己出院後被安排到當地政府部門上班，變相監控，強調自己並無精神病，是被當局強制送入醫院。而她的父親董建彪表示，仍然被當局禁止他與女兒聯絡或見面。<br />\n<br />\n「我不想再過這樣的生活了，要麼就是死嘛。在這種強壓的監控之下，我確實。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n「我工作的自由，我選擇朋友交往的自由，我現在所有的自由都沒有，都被限制了。我跟誰去交往他們都要打聽，都要問。」而她平日的工作，就是打打電話、抄抄寫寫這一類。董在片中又多次反問，自己做錯了甚麼，精神是否真的有問題，「在潑墨前，我還在上海一家單位工作，可以去詢問我的那些同事，我的精神出了問題嗎？」最後她強調自己是「一個很正常的人」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nMHzeKFFqx-sjA6h7ICicFKzk5c=/1018x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LRJFEL7ALJBYTOERV6JXA2IMLE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnMHzeKFFqx-sjA6h7ICicFKzk5c%3D%2F1018x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLRJFEL7ALJBYTOERV6JXA2IMLE.jpg&h=a413944c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■董瑤瓊在出院後首度發佈影片，稱自己精神沒問題。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YrxFRiu2xhRgKRSsS7ZWdVeAzHE=/1579x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HIJZ2XMGZZAALAZDL6OISJ3KSU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYrxFRiu2xhRgKRSsS7ZWdVeAzHE%3D%2F1579x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHIJZ2XMGZZAALAZDL6OISJ3KSU.jpg&h=4b5cfc26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■董瑤瓊2018年因向習近平肖像潑墨，被政府送入精神病院。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不允許與父親聯絡<br />\n<br />\n董瑤瓊的人身自由受到嚴重限制外，就連與父親聯絡都不被允許。董瑤瓊的父親董建彪指出，現在政府不允許女兒離開當地，亦禁止他與董瑤瓊聯絡或見面，同時不准他在網上發表言論。今年他見了女兒兩次，一次是今年一月，第二次就是今年8月，但只是短暫探望了十分鐘。「她有時候會哭，我說想用手機幫她拍照，但她當時非常恐懼」，前妻亦稱女兒在家中會又哭又叫，有時會胡言亂語。<br />\n<br />\n董建彪工作的煤礦坑在前幾。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/j4zavR1lL95n03ufnWLQEjbrbzU=/1179x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XY2W3RHXFBENBBR3RPDZINMK3Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fj4zavR1lL95n03ufnWLQEjbrbzU%3D%2F1179x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXY2W3RHXFBENBBR3RPDZINMK3Q.jpg&h=1ff02de7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■董建彪（右）曾為女兒維權而被帶走。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「逼異議人士到絕境」<br />\n<br />\n人權組織「中國人權捍衞者」研究與倡議顧問藍寧表示，董瑤瓊的影片顯示，中國異見人士一旦被中國政府盯上後，生活的每個層面都會受到嚴重的打壓。「中國政府會想辦法把異議人士逼到絕境，他們無法自己找工作，也無法自己去交朋友。」<br />\n<br />\n現年30歲的董瑤瓊在2018年，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者昨晚發現，董瑤瓊在Twitter上傳包括影片的三個帖文已被刪走。民運人士相林隨後在Twitter表示，他一早預料董的帖文會被刪走，估計這不是她個人意願。<br />\n<br />\n德國之聲/《蘋果》記者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Eos6o5W5hr7Dh2uCASIDF1ShDCc=/363x935/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SK4AQQZITNCJRK2ETHNC4TB4WE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEos6o5W5hr7Dh2uCASIDF1ShDCc%3D%2F363x935%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSK4AQQZITNCJRK2ETHNC4TB4WE.jpg&h=6b4aace9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27a38a44682dc63d90bd4a33719400c6c13a4726","tid":2311620,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T08:17:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ddfb465fca19214ab467f41485ea9905e5eaac","tid":2311620,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T08:18:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01da56eacc3973cec80ce1f0ad1f7f6498da912b","tid":2311620,"uid":371606,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T08:37:12.000Z","msg":"這就是共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}